  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST THE SEQUEL NOW!</h1><p></p><br><h1>PLAY THE FRIENDS WE LEFT BEHIND NEXT!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>A psychological horror game about being a child in an insane asylum. You're in a cruel world but your imaginary friends have your back.</strong><br><br>It's 1949, and you're a new patient at Hathmoore Children's Asylum. During your stay, you'll explore and discover disturbing secrets, including the mysterious Ghost of the Asylum. Along the way, you will befriend other children and their imaginary friends. Together, you will uncover a dark conspiracy where you are to receive a terrible fate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643930/extras/0bbd03d826f2c7c2be76d82fdaab615c.poster.avif?t=1763784441\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643930/extras/0bbd03d826f2c7c2be76d82fdaab615c.webm?t=1763784441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643930/extras/0bbd03d826f2c7c2be76d82fdaab615c.mp4?t=1763784441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Average playtime of 3-4 hours<br></li><li>Atmospheric environment and realistic graphics<br></li><li>Elements of exploration, stealth, platforming, and ARG<br></li><li>Immersive storytelling, dialogue, cutscenes, and lore</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>A psychological horror game about being a child in an insane asylum. You're in a cruel world but your imaginary friends have your back.</strong><br><br>It's 1949, and you're a new patient at Hathmoore Children's Asylum. During your stay, you'll explore and discover disturbing secrets, including the mysterious Ghost of the Asylum. Along the way, you will befriend other children and their imaginary friends. Together, you will uncover a dark conspiracy where you are to receive a terrible fate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643930/extras/0bbd03d826f2c7c2be76d82fdaab615c.poster.avif?t=1763784441\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643930/extras/0bbd03d826f2c7c2be76d82fdaab615c.webm?t=1763784441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643930/extras/0bbd03d826f2c7c2be76d82fdaab615c.mp4?t=1763784441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Average playtime of 3-4 hours<br></li><li>Atmospheric environment and realistic graphics<br></li><li>Elements of exploration, stealth, platforming, and ARG<br></li><li>Immersive storytelling, dialogue, cutscenes, and lore</li></ul>",
